
<h2>TP-Server 0.0.1 released</h2>
<p>by Lee</p>
<p>
	I have just tagged and released 0.0.1 of the Thousand Parsec
	Server, written in C++.  The tag in the CVS is CPP_SERVER_0_0_1.
	You can download it from <a href="downloads.php">here</a>.
</p>
<p>
	The server currently support the initial parts of TP01 Protocol,
	which allows clients to connect and login.  The protocol is
	documented <a href="protocol.php">here</a>.  This means that
	the server is at Milestone Alpha.
</p>

